+ Class Methods

++ Public

* Solar_Sql_Adapter_Mssql::buildSelect() -- Adds a LIMIT clause (or equivalent) to a SELECT statement.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter_Mssql::createSequence() -- Creates a sequence, optionally starting at a certain number.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter_Mssql::dropIndex() -- Drops an index.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter_Mssql::dropSequence() -- Drops a sequence.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter_Mssql::listTables() -- Returns a list of database tables.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter_Mssql::nextSequence() -- Gets a sequence number; creates the sequence if it does not exist.

