* Solar_Sql_Adapter::buildCreateTable() -- Builds a CREATE TABLE command string.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter::commit() -- Commit a transaction and return to autocommit mode.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter::exec() -- Prepares and executes an SQL statement with bound data.

* Solar_Base::locale() -- Looks up locale strings based on a key.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter::nativeColTypes() -- Returns a list of native column types.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter::quote() -- Safely quotes a value for an SQL statement.

* Solar_Sql_Adapter::rollback() -- Roll back a transaction and return to autocommit mode.

